e plot</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many mysterious legends circulate in the world, one of which is about the Cat Tower. It is said that in that unknown corner, a towering structure rises into the clouds, the final resting place and destination for all cats, a sanctuary where their souls find peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;It's called the Cat Tower, so it must be a place only cats can go.&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;What if I became a cat...&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a story about a human who accidentally stumbles into the Cat Tower, encounters and reunites with the cats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A vibrant Maine Coon in a dilapidated amusement park, a ragdoll living in a candy house built atop paradise, and the supreme god who controls the Cat Tower.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Shouldn't cats be a bunch of fluffy, cute little creatures? Why are they all beautiful girls?!&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3929580/extras/cf59183585b10d53f5580854c2b06063.poster.avif?t=1774656680\" width=1170 height=638 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3929580/extras/cf59183585b10d53f5580854c2b06063.webm?t=1774656680\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3929580/extras/cf59183585b10d53f5580854c2b06063.mp4?t=1774656680\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players are transformed into a strange cat who finds themselves in a magical cat tower. Following the storyline, players must defeat the cat leader, explore the cats' inner worlds, develop deeper relationships with the catgir